    termsText: `By visiting this website and/or placing an order, you agree to these Terms of Service. You must be at least 18 years old, or the age of majority in your jurisdiction. We may change products, limit quantities, refuse service, or cancel suspicious or erroneous orders. Pricing and product descriptions may be updated without notice. Shipping timelines are estimates only, and delays caused by customs, carriers, taxes, weather, or incorrect customer details are outside our control. Risk transfers upon delivery. For EU/EEA/Switzerland consumers, mandatory local consumer protections and withdrawal rights apply according to applicable law. All website content (logos, text, images, graphics, and code) is protected intellectual property and may not be copied or redistributed without written consent. To the fullest extent permitted by law, our liability is limited to the amount paid for the relevant order. These terms are governed by the laws of Singapore, without prejudice to mandatory consumer protections in your local jurisdiction.`, privacyText: `This Privacy Policy applies to users in the EU, EEA, Switzerland, the United States, and other supported regions. We collect data you provide (name, email, phone number, shipping/billing details, and order information) and technical data collected automatically (IP address, browser/device data, cookies, and usage data). We process data for order fulfilment, customer service, fraud prevention, legal compliance, and service improvement; legal bases include contract, legal obligation, legitimate interests, and consent where required. We may share data with payment processors, shipping partners, IT providers, and support platforms only as needed, and we do not sell personal data. For users in California and other US states with similar laws, rights may include access, deletion, correction, opt-out rights where applicable, and non-discrimination. For EU/EEA/Swiss users, rights include access, rectification, erasure, restriction, objection, portability, and consent withdrawal. We retain data only as long as necessary for operations, tax/accounting obligations, and legal dispute handling. Where data is transferred internationally, we use lawful safeguards including Standard Contractual Clauses where required. Security controls include encryption in transit, access controls, and secure payment integrations; no method is 100% secure.`
